@startuml
title C3 - Processos (Assign Allowed Vessel Types)

start
:Receive Create/UpdateDockDTO with AllowedVesselTypeIds;
:For each id -> query VesselType repository;
if (VesselType exists?) then (yes)
  :Add to Dock.AllowedVesselTypes;
else (no)
  :Return 400 Bad Request (invalid vessel type id);
endif
:Persist Dock;
:Return DockDTO;
stop

@enduml
